dBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:59:40.000Z","msg":"立法會"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:01:05.000Z","msg":"選埋下屆立會嫁啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:12:40.000Z","msg":"2020立會選舉前應該有新一輪下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:17:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/faq.html#9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voterregistration.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Ffaq.html%239&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV0wfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=e023af28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/faq.html#9</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>問九 : 我在2020年7月底才滿十八歲，而2020年的選民新登記限期則是5月2日，我現在可不可以先登記做選民？<br />\n<br />\n答九 : 2020年正式選民登記冊將在2020年7月25日或之前發表。若你在該日期或之前年滿十八歲，又是香港永久性居民，就符合資格，現在已可以申請登記做選民。 </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來仲登記得<br />\n即係原來冇比人fake<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7231cea8cd269dffacd21e2636fda43c5e6fc18","tid":1756444,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3313e030fe9785ef4d1671d6f60fefcbdacd2c","tid":1756444,"uid":62151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:50:06.000Z","msg":"2020年正式選民登記冊將在2020年7月25日或之前發表。若你在該日期或之前年滿十八歲，又是香港永久性居民，就符合資格，現在已可以申請登記做選民。"},{"pid":"173eccde55d8336333af9e3e724f743c0bdff30a","tid":1756444,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93232fbd656b68abed6741b11cc082412d5b471","tid":1756444,"uid":143183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:56:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"12cb4749be6023504728f4106634e20e31825baa","tid":1756444,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:57:53.000Z"